{"title":"数字反转","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":128,"url":"http://www.tsinsen.com/A1186","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div id=\"pcont1\" style=\"margin-top:20px; display:block;\">\n"},{"title":"问题描述","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　给定一个整数，请将该数各个位上数字反转得到一个新数。新数也应满足整数的常见形式，即除非给定的原数为零，否则反转后得到的新数的最高位数字不应为零（参见样例 2） 。</div>"},{"title":"输入格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　输入共 1 行，一个整数 N。</div>"},{"title":"输出格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　输出共 1 行，一个整数，表示反转后的新数。</div>"},{"title":"样例输入","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">123</div>"},{"title":"输出样例","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　321</div>"},{"title":"样例输入","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">-380</div>"},{"title":"样例输出","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">-83</div>"},{"title":"数据规模和约定","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　-1,000,000,000 ≤ N≤1,000,000,000。</div>\n\n</div>\n"}]}